details.description: Here at Waterbean Coffee, we always try to stay original and never follow the trends. In a time when most coffee shops focus on getting the customers in and out of their doors the quickest, we try to give them a place to relax, hold meetings, go over schoolwork, or just hang out with friends. We want to be more than just another coffee shop. Our founder’s international background brings a unique aspect to the space that most people don’t have. This is reflected from our menu options all the way down to our store designs. One of Tony’s favorite quotes is from Henry Ford: “Quality means doing it right when no one is looking.”

reviews_data.review_text: Great place to be, the staff is very friendly and accommodating!
Love this coffee shop!  All the baristas are professional and courteous!  My favorite coffee shop hands down!  Best baristas, service and atmosphere!

I’m a little disappointed, usually the employees are really cool when I come in. This new one today was a bit rude. She didn’t great me, she fixed my food and just placed it on the counter without calling me up to collect it so I didn’t realize my food was sitting there uncovered for 5 ish minutes. She sat back and got on her phone. I just smiled at her and grabbed it. I thought maybe she was having a bad day and to not agitate it. It wasn’t until, a customer came in after me and she greeted her-and showed her the upmost respect…it was interesting. I hate to admit it but I immediately went to race because I am a black woman and the lady after me was white. So I wanted to not that here, I also will say this-I always come here and never seen her until today. I also am not a rude person so even when I felt the respect wasn’t there, I still tipped and smiled. I am not sure of the employees name but she has like dark blue hair with bangs and piercings.
Nice low key spot on a Friday morning. Great dirty chai!

Lousy staff. Lazy staff. She said she was too busy to make an avocado toast. when I was the ONLY customer in the store and she was on her phone the whole time.
Maybe this is just a front - because they do t care about real customers. Perhaps just a $$laundering outlet
Waterbean is just delightful. Every drink and food item I've tried has become a new favorite. Staff are always friendly and environment is always on point.

To the manager: while it is admirable that you hire high school kids to work there, please, please, please tell them to have the decency to not serve coffee at room temperature. I made the mistake of getting take out coffee here twice and when I was driving away I realized it was room temp and not the least bit hot. Not a serious coffee shop.

Normally I don’t leave reviews but after coming here a few times and been handed the wrong food item I’ve ordered- I’m leaving a review. Great location, quiet. Usually not terribly busy however, it’s a 50/50 shot on whether or not I’ll get my bagel or right (today I was handed a croissant). I know it’s a coffee shop, but this seems like plain laziness. I’ve brought it up before to the girls behind the register but it doesn’t seem to change anything. Just come here for coffee…

Lent, sans intérêt ne personnalité.
Le café était pire que dans une machine automatique.
Le service était déplorable !!!
La serveuse tirait une gueule pas possible !!
Pour avoir un bonjour ou un sourire il fallait payer un supplément.
Elle a eu son pourvoir uniquement parce que est presque obligatoire en États Unis.
Cozy place,  has a nice vibe. Coffee is amazing,  had the latte with double shot, has a rounded taste
Great frappe at a great price
The cutest spot for coffee! Vibey. Some table space for remote working. My iced lavender latte was excellent.

I frequent this spot often on my way to work, but lately it has taken significantly longer to get a single drink. They only have one person working most days which results in long wait times.
I’d recommend visiting if you are planning to stay and work.
One of my favorite and consistent coffee shops in CLT

The dragon matcha tasted like water, wasted my money trying this for the first time. Should have just gone to Starbucks and got the lavender Matcha. I had originally wanted a different drink from the menu and the girl didn’t even know how to make it either so I tried this drink. Atmosphere of the place is good, just need better staff training.
Food is good, coffee is a little weak
cute little coffee shop, great pastries and coffee. also kind staff
My go to for breakfast & coffee.
Waterbean has several choices of espresso beans.
The best cappuccino in town. I love the espresso bean options. The staff is also always pleasant and helpful.

If you can stay away from this place, it takes forever for the coffee to come out and they do not know what they’re doing or what drinks are what! After waiting for 15 minutes for 2 iced coffee was handed 2 coffee that the employees did not know which is coffee was mine! Waste of time and money!!!!!
Love the atmosphere of this place. Some of the best food I’ve had at a coffee shop, and the coffees are addicting. Not very pricey either compared to other coffee places.
Delicious coffee, always a friendly and helpful team working at this location!
A very nice coffee shop. Latte was excellent. Atmosphere is pretty and bright. Very clean too. Comfortable chairs. I will go back. Prices comparable to "the big chain".
Delicious coffee. Cute setting

This small-ish coffee spot is settled in the corner of a nice plaza - the coffee & choices of lattes are ah-mazing, staff super friendly (the guy barista moreso) & super clean with an awesome playlist.

Great place for coffee and getting some computer work done.  They have many locations throughout Charlotte.  This location is small but has both indoor and outdoor seating.   They have gluten-free bakery options as well. I spent a few hours here getting work done. I'll be back.
No greeting when walked in… didn’t seem like a warm and friendly place. Coffee wasn’t good either … won’t be back.

Me and my three friends came in today and it was an amazing experience. Great service from the gal with the red hair. She was very clear spoken and patient with us while we tried to decide what to get. Recommended 10/10!
Place was mad chill. Staff kept it 100 on god. Definitely get the chocolate milk

I walked in. No smile and no greeting . I ordered a Cortado and the girl said which bean. I was impressed that they had different beans but I received a Cappuccino. I tried to explain to the girl it was a one to one ratio and she wanted to argue w me that she gave me less milk even though it was it the cappuccino cup w the same milk as a cappuccino. The young girls seemed to have an attitude and didn’t want to hear the reasoning of my wrong order. This place won’t last.

The staff is super awesome here I don’t know the person’s name who made this latte but keep them. I wanted to try the rose flavor latte and the sample saved me that wasn’t for me. However, they made me this super delicious lavender drink and that was super tasty thank you! I would recommend and definitely come back to this place.

This place is doing it right, Super comfortable chairs, not crowded, Quiet enough for work calls, Fast Wi-Fi, outdoor seating, nice barstools, feels clean and modern. Great coffee also offers coffee tasting flights which is unique. Heavy focus on bean variety and bean sourcing.
Noramally, good coffee. However, my coffee and daughter's Chai did not meet our expectedion. Possible new employees are not fully trained? So, today was a disappointment 😞
Not huge but the coffee is good and not a bad spot to hang for a bit when I'm in the area
The baristas here are all very nice and good at their jobs, especially the young man with the brown curly hair! I recommend a lavender mint latte here.
Best cold brew ever and an extremely clean and friendly experience.

Beautiful ambience and modern stylish decor. Finally places in Charlotte start looking chick and upscale!!! I got their new drink called Wilderness Latte and it was so so good! I will definitely come back here again. Free parking.  Wheelchair ♿️ accessible.  Friendly staff. Great selection of drinks and snacks.
Very clean, very well lit. Customer service was amazing & the coffee was even better! Plenty to choose from, & no way you could go wrong with any choice!

reviews_data.review_text: The coffee was fresh and had a really good taste.The place looked beautiful inside. Definitely recommend.
Can't stay away, can't get enough!

Darn nice latte. Friendly employee on my visit. Zero complaints.

Nice to know this little coffee shop is tucked away in this quasi-hidden spot.
The place is pretty but the coffee was not good at all.
Latte is good
Beautiful place and great customer service. Thank you so much!

I've visited twice and I love this Waterbean location. Wifi with password is consistent for work, including multiple conference calls. Plenty of seating and outlets at every table. Great customer service. Nice set of food options for breakfast/lunch, and not just pastries/break - there are hot and cold sandwiches, at least one of which is veggie. Clean restroom. Convenient location with plenty of parking in the Quail Corners shopping center. Try the coffee with that awesome little chocolate bean, as well as the various tea options which you can sample by scent right there at the counter. It's clean. Apple Pay. The music playlist sounds a lot like my own personal playlist (as of Oct 2022) - Cleo Sol, Solange, Pip Millett, etc. Well-played on all angles, Waterbean. WELL-PLAYED.

Great atmosphere, great coffee, great baristas. Comfortable indoor and outdoor seating, including a bar with cushioned bar stools. Nice NotNeutral dishes. A wide selection of single-origin and blended coffee selections. I was looking for a bean to buy to do home espresso with. Fortunately for me, they offer an "Espresso Flight," three different espresso shots for when you can't make up your mind. The two baristas were very welcoming and knowledgeable, giving their opinions on the various beans, sharing their preferences and how/what they brew at home, to help me find the right choice. And when they brewed espressos, going from one coffee to another, they took the time to make sure to dial it in right to present a quality drink, well-worth the time and money.
Good coffee, good food. Aesthetics is 🤌🏻. This place inspires me to get out of the house and do some work.
Super nice! Great coffee, nice staff!
